2015-07~07
http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/general/628492/rights-group-slams-china-tv-report-on-repatriated-uighurs

Bangkok Post
People being deported from Thailand are seen brought off an airplane by police at an unidentified location in China on July 9 in this file still image taken from CCTV video aired on July 11. (Reuters photo)
The report came as China makes efforts to keep its ethnic Uighurs from leaving the country. Hundreds, perhaps thousands of members of the largely Muslim ethnic minority have left China in recent years, clandestinely crossing into Southeast Asia before making their way to Turkey.

